09/14/79  remove_graphics, rg

Syntax:  rg {switch1 ... switchN} {-control_args}


Function:  Detaches the graphics I/O switches attached by setup_graphics.


Arguments:
switchI
   are names of specific graphics I/O switches to detach.  (DEFAULT-- all
   graphics I/O switches attached by setup_graphics.)


Control arguments:
-all, -a
   specifies that all graphics I/O switches attached by setup_graphics are to
   be detached.  (DEFAULT if no switchI arguments are given)
